{"tid":384343,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件委屈的事","createTime":"2017-09-02T08:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T10:48:30.000Z","uid":76247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"addf27ec7ce15f02e85b0c7219c4c0c6e1515f49","tid":384343,"uid":76247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:31:17.000Z","msg":"係人都知依家膠袋要收費<br />\n有個中年男人黎買嘢 <br />\n跟著佢自己偷偷地好鬼祟咁拎左個膠袋<br />\n<br />\n埋單嘅時候 佢俾左岩岩好嘅錢但未俾膠袋錢<br />\n咁我就話：先生 唔好意思仲差膠袋收費<br />\n點知佢大大聲話：我依家有話唔俾錢咩？（跟著佢先響褲袋拎錢出嚟）<br />\n我： 唔好意思啊 多謝曬 byebye <br />\n跟著反話我： 你咁嘅態度就唔得啦 我依家有話唔俾咩 你咁對客人都有？ 學下禮貌啦<br />\n<br />\n雖然係好小事 但你明明係唔想俾膠袋錢想鬼鬼崇祟拎一個 反而話番我態度有問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfe663768e321040ea2bf89e9e1d8f014f44bdd","tid":384343,"uid":27320,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:33:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"630daf15b150f3e44222748d0eefe14cc5a029c3","tid":384343,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:39:38.000Z","msg":"More"},{"pid":"c2b86b016edd7645b69ca32f953c95fb8006d704","tid":384343,"uid":27320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:47:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"951a88f3c79c535a4feb349cb286020fe9ef65ee","tid":384343,"uid":76247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}